com.trolltech.qt.QtJambiInterface
public class Course
extends com.trolltech.qt.gui.QListWidgetItem

Holds all the information about course. Holds the course code, name, id, lecture, seminar and seminarChosen. One object represents whole course as extension of QListWidgetItem with all information which are needed for its rendering in the List courses.

Version:
2012-06-04
Author:
Michal Kimle
